data.description: Welcome to the Best Value in Double Tree West! This updated home offers a perfect blend of style and functionality, showcasing beautiful new hardwood floors throughout. The open-concept living, dining, and kitchen area is bathed in natural light, creating a cheerful atmosphere.The living room features vaulted ceilings, a fireplace, and a neutral color palette, providing a cozy and sophisticated space. The dining and kitchen combo boasts stainless appliances and sliders leading to a spacious deck, seamlessly connecting indoor and outdoor living.Three bedrooms, including a primary with ensuite, complete the first floor. The lower level adds versatility with a fourth bedroom, additional living space, and a full bathroom. Updates throughout ensure a cohesive and appealing aesthetic. The property is nestled in the desirable Double Tree West neighborhood, offering a friendly community, excellent schools, and proximity to many amenities. Tonal Workout system is included in Sale!
